al=\u0421\u0420\u0411\u0418 \u041d\u0410 \u041a\u041e\u0421\u041e\u0412\u0423 \u0418 \u0423 \u041c\u0415\u0422\u041e\u0425\u0418\u0408\u0418|date=27\u201329 May 2005|url=http://www.sanu.ac.rs/Izdanja/SrbiNaKosovu/06ZurovacMirko.pdf|publisher=SANU}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|last1=Schwandner-Sievers|first1=Stephanie|last2=Fischer|first2=Bernd J\u00fcrgen|title=Albanian Identities: Myth and History|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oRASDq3rc-YC&pg=PA60|year=2002|publisher=Indiana University Press|isbn=0-253-34189-2}}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Battle of Kosovo}}\n\n{{Kosovo topics}}\n{{Serbia topics}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n[[Category:Historiography of Serbia]]\n[[Category:History of Kosovo]]\n[[Category:Serbian nationalism]]\n[[Category:Serb traditions]]\n[[Category:Serbian epic poetry]]\n[[Category:Serbian folklore]]\n[[Category:Myth of origins]]\n[[Category:Revenge]]\n[[Category:Martyrdom]]\n[[Category:Christianity and Islam]]\n[[Category:National mysticism]]\n[[Category:Religious nationalism]]\n[[Category:Political history of Serbia]]\n[[Category:History of the Serbs]]\n[[Category:National symbols of Serbia]]\n", "name_user": "96.255.215.218", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eOutside of Serbia and Reception:Unnecesary)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kosovo_Myth"}
