 ''[[Nucula tokyoensis]]'' Yokoyama, 1920\n* ''[[Nucula torresi]]'' E. A. Smith, 1885\n* ''[[Nucula trigonica]]'' Lan & Lee, 2001\n* ''[[Nucula tumidula]]'' <small>(Malm, 1860)</small>    \n* ''[[Nucula venezuelana]]'' Weisbord, 1964\n* ''[[Nucula vincentiana]]'' (Cotton & Godfrey, 1938)\n* ''[[Nucula zophos]]'' <small>A. H. Clark, 1960</small>  \n{{div col end}}\n\n==Extinct species==\nExtinct species within the genus ''Nucula'' include:<ref name=AA>[http://fossilworks.org/bridge.pl?action=taxonInfo&taxon_no=16082 Fossilworks]</ref>\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n*''[[Nucula alcocki|N. alcocki]]'' \u2020 <small>Noetling 1895</small>\n*''[[Nucula andersoni|N. andersoni]]'' \u2020 <small>Clark & Durham 1946</small>\n*''[[Nucula assiniboiensis|N. assiniboiensis]]'' \u2020 <small>Russell & Landes 1937</small>\n*''[[Nucula athabaskensis|N. athabaskensis]]'' \u2020 <small>McLearn 1931</small>\n*''[[Nucula brewsterensis|N. brewsterensis]]'' \u2020 <small>Hassan 1953</small>\n*''[[Nucula cancellata|N. cancellata]]'' \u2020 <small>Meek & Hayden 1857</small>\n*''[[Nucula cancellata|N. cancellata]]'' \u2020 <small>Vredenburg 1928</small>\n*''[[Nucula catalina|N. catalina]]'' \u2020 <small>Olsson 1930</small>\n*''[[Nucula chrysocoma|N. chrysocoma]]'' \u2020 <small>Dall 1908</small>\n*''[[Nucula cilleborgensis|N. cilleborgensis]]'' \u2020 <small>Ravn 1907</small>\n*''[[Nucula concinna|N. concinna]]'' \u2020 <small>Sowerby 1836</small>\n*''[[Nucula cossmanni|N. cossmanni]]'' \u2020 <small>Vincent 1892</small>\n*''[[Nucula costaeimbricatus|N. costaeimbricatus]]'' \u2020 <small>Newton 1922</small>\n*''[[Nucula crepida|N. crepida]]'' \u2020 <small>Marwick 1931</small>\n*''[[Nucula cunifrons|N. cunifrons]]'' \u2020 <small>Conrad 1860</small>\n*''[[Nucula domandaensis|N. domandaensis]]'' \u2020 <small>Eames 1951</small>\n*''[[Nucula gabbiana|N. gabbiana]]'' \u2020 <small>Dickerson 1916</small>\n*''[[Nucula greppina|N. greppina]]'' \u2020 <small>Deshayes 1858</small>\n*''[[Nucula major|N